(377, '_transient_dash_4077549d03da2e451c8b5f002294ff51', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2016/04/coleman/''>WordPress 4.5 “Coleman”</a> <span class="rss-date">12.04.2016</span><div class="rssSummary">Version 4.5 of WordPress, named “Coleman” in honor of jazz saxophonist Coleman Hawkins, is available for download or update in your WordPress dashboard. New features in 4.5 help streamline your workflow, whether you’re writing or building your site. Editing Improvements Inline Linking Stay focused on your writing with a less distracting interface that keeps</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/3-signs-your-wordpress-development-team-is-not-actually-a-team'' title=''This post was contributed by guest author Peter Suhm. Peter is a web developer from the Land of the Danes. He is the creator of WP Pusher and a huge travel addict, bringing his work along with him as he goes.   If you run a typical WordPress agency, I will be bold enough to say this: Your WordPress team is probably not working as a team. Ouch! Developer prod''>WPTavern: 3 Signs Your WordPress Development Team Is Not Actually a Team</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/font-awesome-4-6-0-adds-new-accessibility-icons-category'' title=''Font Awesome creator Dave Gandy announced the release of version 4.6.0 this week. The open source vector icon collection is used on approximately 60 million websites, including high profile sites like whitehouse.gov, thebeatles.com, and washingtonpost.com. Additionally, more than 300 plugins on WordPress.org and dozens of themes use Font Awesome in some way.''>WPTavern: Font Awesome 4.6.0 Adds New Accessibility Icons Category</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/simple-cache-a-new-one-click-install-caching-plugin-for-wordpress'' title=''WordPress caching plugins are notorious for being packed full of confusing options, spammy with upsells, and difficult to uninstall. Users who are looking for a caching solution that simply works and has nothing to configure should check out Simple Cache, a new plugin on WordPress.org that offers a one-click install. The plugin promises lightning fast speed''>WPTavern: Simple Cache: A New One-Click Install Caching Plugin for WordPress</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Популярный плагин:</span> <a href=''https://wordpress.org/plugins/ml-slider/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>Meta Slider</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=ml-slider&amp;_wpnonce=e1f1f91936&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Meta Slider''>Установить</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
